      "text": [
        ": \"لاَ يَتَزَوَّجُ اَلْيَهُودِيَّةَ وَ لاَ اَلنَّصْرَانِيَّةَ عَلَى حُرَّةٍ مُتْعَةً وَ غَيْرَ مُتْعَةٍ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4588 - It is narrated from Sadan, from Abu Basir, from Abu Abdillah (as), who said:\n\"A man should not marry a Jewish or Christian woman alongside a free Muslim woman, whether in Mutah (temporary marriage) or in a permanent marriage.\""
        ]
